('tj', 'Math/Quant', 'Priya drove to a friend''s house at 40 mph and returned along the same route at 35 mph. What was the average speed for the round trip?', '["35 mph", "37.5 mph", "40 mph", "37.3 mph"]'::jsonb, 3, 'For equal distances at two speeds, average speed is the harmonic mean: 2(40)(35)/(40+35) = 37.3 mph. ✓'),
