('tj', 'Math/Quant', 'Two 3-Ohm resistors R1 and R2 are in parallel between terminals a and b. Terminal b connects to c, and two more 3-Ohm resistors R3, R4 are in series between c and d. What is the net resistance between a and d?', '["4.5 Ohms", "12 Ohms", "9 Ohms", "7.5 Ohms"]'::jsonb, 3, 'R1∥R2 = 3/2 = 1.5 Ohms. R3+R4 in series = 6 Ohms. Since b and c are joined, total = 1.5 Ohms + 6 Ohms = 7.5 Ohms. ✓'),
