('acl', 'Math/Quant', 'If it is 6:00 am in Detroit, it''s 3:30 pm in Mumbai. A flight takes 17 hours to Mumbai and leaves Detroit at 2:30 pm on March 10. When does it land in Mumbai?', '["March 10 at 11:00 pm", "March 11 at 11:00 am", "March 11 at 1:00 pm", "March 11 at 5:00 pm"]'::jsonb, 3, 'Mumbai is 9.5 hours ahead. Landing Detroit-time = 2:30pm + 17h = 7:30am (Mar 11). Convert to Mumbai time: 7:30am + 9:30 = 5:00pm March 11. ✓'),
